{"title":"抗议书","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗议书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿拉伯人是狮子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道还怕纸老虎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狮子呀阿拉伯人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶走那群美国驴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊拉克和黎巴嫩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点起战斗的火炬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金字塔就是战旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地中海就是战鼓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的手是矛头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指向贝鲁特港口——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对强盗要用宝刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对豺狼要用斧头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝鲁特是火山口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是强盗的墓窟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬要是不滚走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就得抛下他的骨头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上甘岭可以作证，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼龙弹衣护不了身；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏伊士可以作证，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎寸步难行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎巴嫩的旗子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说是有一棵树；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这棵树挥动起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎马上就戳穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬戴的钢盔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉下地就成泥土；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他们的钢盔里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们栽上自由树。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎掉到海里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上帝也没法救他；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想要留一条命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就得悬崖勒马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴格达的义旗举起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠上面鲜花开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为自由而战的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友遍于全世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石可烂，海可枯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿拉伯一定要自由；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和阿拉伯朋友——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗中握起手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕中国人民志愿军用美国侵略者的钢盔栽上花和小树。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}